-- Sigma Says Aspen Hasn't Made Formal Proposal, Will Continue Due Diligence
-- Victoria Batchelor
-- 2010-07-05T23:03:09Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-05/sigma-says-aspen-hasn-t-made-formal-proposal-will-continue-due-diligence.html

          
          
             Sigma Pharmaceuticals Ltd. has been
advised by Aspen Pharmacare Holdings Ltd. that it wishes to
continue its due diligence review.  
 “Aspen has not made any formal proposal to Sigma and Sigma
continues to recommend that shareholders take no action at this
time,” the company said in a statement.  
          
          


  


        